CatDescriptText: Cutline of related article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 30, 1946, pg. 26 reads: "Former GIs will be in preponderance at the Centre Avenue YMCA's All-Star boxing show, being held at the Centre Avenue YMCA this Friday, Nov. 29, featuring Charley Burley as guest referee."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four male boxers, including unknown, Jimmy Eichelberger, Bob Lundy, and Charley Burley, standing in boxing ring in Centre Avenue YMCA for All-Star boxing show
